'''克里斯·魏茲'''（{{lang-en|Christopher John Weitz}}，{{bd|1969年|11月30日}}）<ref>The most accurate source of Weitz's birth date is the 1969 given in the production notes on the DVD for "Chuck & Buck." A check of the database at ancestry.com will give greater detail.</ref>是一名[[美国|美国]]电影导演、监制、编剧和演员。他与他哥哥[[保羅·韋茲|保羅·韋茲]]（Paul Weitz）共同导演了喜剧片《[[美国派|美国派]]》和《[[單親插班生|單親插班生]]》，单独导演了奇幻片《[[魔幻羅盤|魔幻羅盤]]》和《[[暮光之城2：新月|暮光之城2：新月]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cinematical.com/2009/12/01/chris-weitz-to-direct-two-part-breaking-dawn-finale/ |title=Chris Weitz to Direct Two-Part 'Breaking Dawn' Finale? |accessdate=2012-02-06 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803133236/http://www.cinematical.com/2009/12/01/chris-weitz-to-direct-two-part-breaking-dawn-finale/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
克里斯·魏茲出生在美國紐約市<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0919363/bio|title=Chris Weitz - Biography|work=IMDb|accessdate=2018-01-05|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803133237/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0919363/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。父親John Weitz是出生在德國的[[猶太人|猶太人]]，是時裝設計師兼小說家<ref>{{cite web|first=Gay|last=Pauley|url=https://www.upi.com/Archives/1983/01/04/Many-facets-of-John-Weitz/2282410504400/|title=Many facets of John Weitz|work=United Press International|date=January 4, 1983|accessdate=April 23, 2018|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803133242/https://www.upi.com/Archives/1983/01/04/Many-facets-of-John-Weitz/2282410504400/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Naomi|last=Pfefferman|url=http://jewishjournal.com/mobile_20111212/101733/|title=Paul Weitz on dads, De Niro and “Being Flynn”|work=Jewish Journal|date=March 5, 2012|accessdate=April 23, 2018|archive-date=2018-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180812171217/http://jewishjournal.com/mobile_20111212/101733/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Naomi|last=Pfefferman|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/92681/|title=An Immigrant Struggles for a ‘Better Life’ for His Son|work=Jewish Journal|date=June 1, 2011|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803135340/https://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/92681/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/07/fashion/mens-style/the-weitz-brothers-help-each-other-through-hollywood-hits-and-misses.html|title=The Weitz Brothers Help Each Other Through Hollywood Hits and Misses|date=June 6, 2015|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-02-06|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803133307/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/07/fashion/mens-style/the-weitz-brothers-help-each-other-through-hollywood-hits-and-misses.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://people.com/archive/john-weitz-vol-38-no-17/|title=John Weitz|date=October 26, 1992|work=People Magazine|accessdate=2018-02-06|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803133305/https://people.com/archive/john-weitz-vol-38-no-17/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。母親Susan Kohner是美國女演員，有[[猶太|猶太]]血統和墨西哥血統<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0463435/bio|title=Susan Kohner - Biography|work=IMDb|accessdate=2018-01-05|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803133315/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0463435/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外祖父Paul Kohner是猶太人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0463434/bio|title=Paul Kohner - Biography|work=IMDb|accessdate=2018-01-28|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803133321/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0463434/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Adrian|last=Florido|url=https://www.npr.org/2016/11/15/502111417/mexican-film-actress-lupita-tovar-dies-at-106|title=Mexican Film Actress Lupita Tovar Dies At 106|work=National Public Radio|date=November 15, 2016|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808073626/https://www.npr.org/2016/11/15/502111417/mexican-film-actress-lupita-tovar-dies-at-106|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Oliver|last=Lyttelton|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2012/04/5-things-you-may-not-know-about-douglas-sirks-imitation-of-life-111627/|title=5 Things You May Not Know About Douglas Sirk’s ‘Imitation Of Life’|work=IndieWire|date=April 17, 2012|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022074233/https://www.indiewire.com/2012/04/5-things-you-may-not-know-about-douglas-sirks-imitation-of-life-111627/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外祖母Lupita Tovar是墨西哥女演員，信奉[[天主教|天主教]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.journalgazette.net/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20071208%2FENT01%2F712080396|title=director “flying blind” with film|date=December 8, 2007|work=The Journal Gazette|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071210010524/http://www.journalgazette.net/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20071208%2FENT01%2F712080396|archivedate=2007年12月10日|accessdate=2018年1月5日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lupita-tovar-dead-dracula-actress-850624|title=Lupita Tovar, Actress in the Spanish-Language Version of 1931's 'Dracula,' Dies at 106|date=November 13, 2016|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2018-02-06|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140905/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lupita-tovar-dead-dracula-actress-850624|dead-url=no}}</ref>。哥哥[[保羅·韋茲|保羅·韋茲]]是電影導演兼編劇。

